_:N708bb35625a94c43a01e9d57a9769b6f <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Katherine Green was appointed Director General for Labour Market and Skills in September 2025. Before that, she was in a jobshare with Sophie Dean as joint Directors General for <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> Policy.</p>\n\n<p>Before <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr>, Katherine and Sophie were Directors General for Borders and Trade in <abbr title=\"HM Revenue and Customs\">HMRC</abbr>. They were responsible for policy and operation of the UK border for goods and delivered the major border change programme for Brexit. Katherine and Sophie joined <abbr title=\"HM Revenue and Customs\">HMRC</abbr> in August 2018 as job share Directors of Customs and Border Design. </p>\n\n<p>Katherine was previously Operations Director at HM Treasury. Prior to that she worked in a variety of policy roles in HM Treasury. </p>\n\n<p>Before joining the Civil Service, Katherine worked in academia.</p>\n\n" .
